{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "我有一個榮美家鄉", "storyInfo": "斯普莉雅單獨行動遭遇當地居民。另一邊，一場事關修道院未來的談話正在展開。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g10_monasterycorridor_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（萊蒙德那傢伙，神神秘秘的......）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（有什麼事情不能現在說，還非要等到晚上啊？）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搞不懂，算了，先不管他了。）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#7$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（今天這麼晚才送吃的過去，蕾繆安小姐大概要餓壞了吧......唉，而且還只有這麼一點。）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hungry"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（爭氣一點，我的肚子！別叫了別叫了，不是剛剛吃過東西嗎！）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唉......）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（真想有一天，能什麼都不管地大吃一頓......）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是誰？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰在那邊？我已經發現你了......！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底是誰躲在那邊？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算不出聲我也知道有人在，我、我看到了！你不是修道院的人！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bullet_loading", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點出來！再、再不出來，我就要喊人......不對，我就要扣下扳機了！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好，我出來。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，失策了......", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你眼睛可真尖，是我的光翼不小心露出來了嗎？我就說我們薩科塔這人人不同款的光環和光翼真的很容易暴露身形......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是的，我還以為在這裡行動不需要那麼謹慎呢。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我之前沒見過你，你是誰？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好啊，女士。先把銃放下吧，這可不是好女孩該用來指著同族的東西。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你也是薩科塔，那你應該能明白吧，我對你完全沒有惡意。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是，呃，這次可以算得上是正義使者？差不多吧，畢竟算是來救人的......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#10$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你不願意說就算了。我現在就喊人來——", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "power": 10.0, "times": 50.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎哎，你別急啊。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "power": 10.0, "times": 50.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔唔唔！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（放開我！）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題，不過你可別真的大叫哦。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——哈......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，有點沒控制住力道。你還好嗎？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳......咳咳，你到底是什麼人，想幹什麼？！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴你也沒什麼，我是來找人的。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來找一個和我們一樣的薩科塔，粉色頭髮，現在應該還坐著輪椅吧，人看起來特別和善，不過其實性格沒那麼好的......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（是蕾繆安小姐？！）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？看你的表情......你們認識？我的運氣還是挺不錯的嘛。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#7$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛端著飯菜，是要給誰送去嗎？我隨便猜猜，難道是送去給蕾繆安的？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嗯？！）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（她是怎麼知道的？？）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我又猜對啦？你的表情也太明顯了！", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那能不能請你告訴我，這位蕾繆安小姐這段時間過得還好嗎？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不想說？還是不能說？你在猶豫，還有點害怕......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你別亂說！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不是亂說，你自己最清楚。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好像有很多煩惱的樣子，真奇怪，我本來以為住在這種與世隔絕的地方，不會有很多煩心事的。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為什麼？因為這裡沒有多少同族，所以和其他人起了爭執嗎？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......和你沒關係。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是嗎？那是因為你手裡那把守護銃看上去好久沒保養，有點生鏽了？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是因為這個的話，我倒是可以幫你哦，我還挺擅長維修銃的呢。只要你告訴我蕾繆安到底在哪裡就行了，是不是很划算？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我吧，你其實也能猜到我是什麼身份，對吧？你看起來挺聰明的。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和蕾繆安小姐一樣，是拉特蘭派來的人？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "答對了。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，閒聊就到此為止。我還趕時間......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的不告訴我蕾繆安在哪嗎？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，既然你不願意說，那就算了。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassclink", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "送吃的這活，就交給我吧。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就這樣，再見啦。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g4_gatheringplace_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_revolver"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一個，這樣就行了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些人是......強盜？還挺能折騰。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科，你那邊怎麼樣？我好像聽到很大的動靜，你沒破壞建築吧？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那太好了。辛苦了，我這邊的也都解決了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太感謝了，你們真的很厲害......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#8$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣一來，那群強盜應該就會老實一陣子了吧。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#8$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽你這麼說，這應該不是你們第一次被騷擾了吧？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們經常遇到這樣的情況嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是從拉特蘭來的，那應該知道到這的路有多難走吧。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是有載具，恐怕我們也沒法順利進入。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了走投無路的人，沒人會願意在這種地方晃蕩。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#8$2"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們也看到了，這片荒野上除了這座修道院外什麼都沒有，那些混帳東西一旦發現我們，怎麼可能會放過。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，現在快入冬了，他們只會來得更勤。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我記得班尼上次右腿傷得不輕，他現在怎麼樣了？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有點瘸，只能熬著。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，對了，這兩位......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是來自拉特蘭的，嗯，應該勉強算是使者吧？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，是拉特蘭來的客人......該怎麼稱呼兩位？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭公證所執行者費德里科。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者里凱萊。我們還有一位同行人，不過她已經先行一步。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科先生，里凱萊先生。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看起來一點也不吃驚。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，因為大家都清楚拉特蘭一定會再派人前來，只不過沒有人能確定來的會是什麼樣的客人。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來還以為......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高瘦文弱的中年人不自覺地看向兩名拉特蘭來客手中的銃。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來以為拉特蘭會直接派人來問罪......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問罪？你們犯了什麼罪？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在中庭公證所，大多數罪犯只要能自首，並取得行為對象的諒解，都可以獲得減刑。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自、自首？減刑？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈？你這混帳在說什麼？！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，費德里科！現在情況還不明，這些都等找到蕾繆安和奧倫之後再說。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我們想見這裡的負責人，能麻煩你通報一下嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，好的！請稍等，我這就去......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必了。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝兩位的幫助，你們要找的人是我。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，來遲一步。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教閣下！還有杰拉爾德......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杰拉爾德老大！", "name": "萊蒙德"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您就是這座修道院的主教閣下？這位，呃，杰拉爾德先生也是這裡的負責人嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不是。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我確實不是那麼了不起的人物。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道各位一定有許多問題想問。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請移步，讓我們換一個更適合的地方談話。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g7_chapel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒，請把大門關上，暫時不要讓其他人靠近這裡。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，主教閣下......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有我在。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德，你繼續去做你該做的。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......行，老大你多小心。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就在門口等著你們......有什麼事的話，隨時可以叫我。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，這樣就不會有人打擾了。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是這裡的主教斯特凡諾·托雷格羅薩，兼任這座修道院的院長。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位客人遠道而來，招待不周......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必進行無意義的寒暄。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "受教宗伊萬杰利斯塔十一世閣下囑託，我與同僚前來尋找兩位拉特蘭特使。請回答：蕾繆安與奧倫·亞吉奧拉斯身處何處？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想我只能告訴你......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安特使正在修道院內做客。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請不用擔心，我們不會無禮地對待客人，她非常安全。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有提及奧倫·亞吉奧拉斯。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫特使的下落......這該是我想要問的才是。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#4$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道不是奧倫特使聯繫了拉特蘭，兩位才會到得如此迅速嗎？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#4$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，主教閣下，這和我們收到的情報有些衝突。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們收到的情報是，位於荒原上的安布羅修修道院向拉特蘭發送了一封求救信，隨後我們向此地派出了兩位特使，但他們雙雙失去聯繫。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，教宗閣下特派我們前來尋人並調查情況......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到這裡為止，與您所知的資訊有什麼衝突的地方嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們沒能留住奧倫特使。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是，奧倫並未被限制行動。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這點我可以作證。那位奧倫特使警戒心很強。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在“邀請”蕾繆安小姐留下做客時，他趁我們的人不注意，自包圍之中逃脫了。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也不清楚他之後去了哪。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫跑了，但不露面，也沒有聯絡。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有點什麼不太好的預感？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你別光“嗯”啊......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有這位披著斗篷的朋友，我想一般居民應該不會知道得這麼多吧，你到底是什麼身份？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是這裡的獵戶代表，兼護衛吧。可以不用在意我。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$2"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，嗯，暫時就當是這麼回事好了......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫的事暫且不提。關於蕾繆安特使，我需要一個合理的解釋。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼修道院會限制一位前來援助的拉特蘭特使的行動？我將根據你的回答，判斷接下來該如何採取行動。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......兩位既然是拉特蘭的使者，應該都清楚這座修道院的背景。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅限於任務資料上有記載的部分。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十多年前......我們為躲避天災而誤入這片荒野，燃料耗盡，整座修道院被困在此處。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法溝通外界，我們只能自己嘗試耕種。但這裡的土壤本就貧瘠，到了今天，地裡已經長不出多少糧食。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅如此，荒原上的野獸以及比野獸更兇殘的劫掠者都是巨大的威脅。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時的我們別無選擇......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，你們選擇收留荒原上的流浪者。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#6$2"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“收留”這個詞太過傲慢。不，不是收留。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是接納那些無家可歸的人。人們因種種緣由失去了可以回去的地方，那我們就再給他們一個。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#4$2"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯特凡諾......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$2"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打斷一下。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一件事情需要確認。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，費德里科，你打算幹什麼......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#7$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ftrub", "volume": 0.9, "delay": 0.6}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.52", "scale": 1.05, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！住手！", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#5$2"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#5$1", "bstart": 0.05, "bend": 0.13, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者閣下！你這是在做什麼！", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確認完畢。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#6$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也太亂來了......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，這還真是個大發現。主教閣下，可以解釋一下這是怎麼一回事嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一座拉特蘭修道院內——", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會有薩卡茲？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這可真是......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果令你不快，我可以道歉。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是什麼人？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好像已經說過了。我只是個獵戶，獵戶杰拉爾德。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可惜了。看來你並不相信。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}